<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: heavy bridge -->
  <HeavyBridge.label>重型桥梁</HeavyBridge.label>
  <!-- EN: A stronger version of the basic bridge which supports heavy structures on top. You can build a whole colony on water with this. -->
  <HeavyBridge.description>这是基础桥梁的强化版，可支撑重型结构。利用这些桥梁可以把整个殖民地搬到水上。</HeavyBridge.description>
  
  <!-- EN: gravship substructure -->
  <Substructure.label>逆重飞船基架</Substructure.label>
  <!-- EN: A lightweight truss structure with flooring on top that forms the deck of a gravship. Only things on top of this substructure can be lifted by the grav engine's levitation field. This floor must be constructed within range of a grav engine.\n\nGravship substructure can be removed using the 'remove foundation' designator. -->
  <Substructure.description>一种轻质支撑结构，其顶部被用作逆重飞船的甲板。只有位于该基架上的物体才能被逆重引擎的悬浮场抬升。此基架必须在逆重引擎的作用范围内建造。\n\n你可以使用“移除地基”指令拆除逆重飞船基架。</Substructure.description>
  
</LanguageData>